      "markText": "因之我们的政事，注重体制的安定，而不计较对一人一事的绝对公允。牺牲少数人，正是维持大局的办法。",
      "totalCount": 19872,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840995&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=14797&rangeEnd=14844",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/091322d05cd5230913042e3?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=14797&rangeEnd=14844"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840995_19_29176-29256",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "29176-29256",
      "markText": "郑氏之所以能赢得万岁的欢心，并不是具有闭月羞花的美貌，而是由于聪明机警，意志坚决，喜欢读书，因而符合皇帝感情上的需要。如果专恃色相，则宠爱决不能如此的历久不衰。",
      "totalCount": 14320,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840995&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=29176&rangeEnd=29256",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/091322d05cd5230913042e3?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=29176&rangeEnd=29256"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840995_19_14854-14902",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "14854-14902",
      "markText": "在这些事例中，张居正的主张无疑都很正确，但是这种铁面无私的态度，在以后也并不是不需要付出代价的。",
      "totalCount": 12405,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840995&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=14854&rangeEnd=14902",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/091322d05cd5230913042e3?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=14854&rangeEnd=14902"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840995_19_25269-25305",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "25269-25305",
      "markText": "皇室的情谊不同于世俗，它不具有世俗友谊的那种由于互相关怀而产生的永久性。",
      "totalCount": 11543,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840995&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=25269&rangeEnd=25305",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/091322d05cd5230913042e3?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=25269&rangeEnd=25305"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840995_20_8302-8342",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "8302-8342",
      "markText": "因为我们的帝国在体制上实施中央集权，其精神上的支柱为道德，管理的方法则依靠文牍。",
      "totalCount": 10512,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840995&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=8302&rangeEnd=8342",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/091322d05cd5230913042e3?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=8302&rangeEnd=8342"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840995_19_21740-21816",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "21740-21816",
      "markText": "统治我们这个庞大帝国，专靠严刑峻法是不可能的，其秘诀在于运用伦理道德的力量使卑下者服从尊上，女人听男人的吩咐，而未受教育的愚民则以读书识字的人作为楷模。",
      "totalCount": 10116,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840995&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=21740&rangeEnd=21816",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/091322d05cd5230913042e3?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=21740&rangeEnd=21816"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840995_21_15862-15962",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "15862-15962",
      "markText": "一个具有高度行政效率的政府，具备体制上技术上的周密，则不致接二连三地在紧急情况下依赖于道德观念作救命的符箓。说得严重一点，后者已不是一种好现象，而是组织机构违反时代，不能在复杂的社会中推陈出新的结果。",
      "totalCount": 9884,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840995&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=15862&rangeEnd=15962",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/091322d05cd5230913042e3?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=15862&rangeEnd=15962"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840995_18_3382-3419",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "3382-3419",
      "markText": "笔者以为，中国两千年来，以道德代替法制，至明代而极，这就是一切问题的症结。",
      "totalCount": 9786,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840995&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=3382&rangeEnd=3419",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/091322d05cd5230913042e3?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=3382&rangeEnd=3419"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840995_19_870-931",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "870-931",
      "markText": "这些事件，表面看来虽似末端小节，但实质上却是以前发生大事的症结，也是将在以后掀起波澜的机缘。其间关系因果，恰为历史的重点。",
      "totalCount": 9396,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840995&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=870&rangeEnd=931",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/091322d05cd5230913042e3?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=870&rangeEnd=931"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840995_19_5003-5063",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "5003-5063",
      "markText": "谁也没有想到，这一小小的插曲，竟是一场影响深远的政治斗争的契机，导致了今后数十年皇帝与臣僚的对立，而且涉及到了整个帝国。",
      "totalCount": 8100,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840995&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=5003&rangeEnd=5063",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/091322d05cd5230913042e3?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=5003&rangeEnd=5063"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840995_18_2067-2122",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "2067-2122",
      "markText": "这种维护落后的农业经济、不愿发展商业及金融的做法，正是中国在世界范围内由先进的汉唐演变为落后的明清的主要原因。",
      "totalCount": 7596,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840995&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=2067&rangeEnd=2122",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/091322d05cd5230913042e3?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=2067&rangeEnd=2122"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840995_19_19881-19936",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "19881-19936",
      "markText": "一个精明的皇帝能够做到让大学士的票拟永远体现自己的意图而不发生争执，这种微妙的关系又少不了秉笔太监的从中协调。",
      "totalCount": 7320,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840995&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=19881&rangeEnd=19936",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/091322d05cd5230913042e3?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=19881&rangeEnd=19936"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840995_19_31038-31046",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "31038-31046",
      "markText": "大风起于青萍之末",
      "totalCount": 7014,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840995&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=31038&rangeEnd=31046",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/091322d05cd5230913042e3?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=31038&rangeEnd=31046"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840995_19_5219-5280",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "5219-5280",
      "markText": "这种珠帘是一种有趣的道具，它们在皇帝的眼前脑后来回晃动，使他极不舒服，其目的就在于提醒他必须具有端庄的仪态，不能轻浮造次。",
      "totalCount": 6968,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840995&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=5219&rangeEnd=5280",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/091322d05cd5230913042e3?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=5219&rangeEnd=5280"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840995_22_21220-21267",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "21220-21267",
      "markText": "万历皇帝缺乏坚强的意志和决心，但并不缺乏清醒和机灵的头脑，然而他竟欣然接受了这种精神上的活埋。",
      "totalCount": 6783,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840995&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=21220&rangeEnd=21267",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/091322d05cd5230913042e3?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=21220&rangeEnd=21267"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840995_20_17018-17060",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "17018-17060",
      "markText": "这些人把正直当作商品，甚至不惜用诽谤讪议人君的方法作本钱，然后招摇贩卖他正直的声望。",
      "totalCount": 6735,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840995&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=17018&rangeEnd=17060",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/091322d05cd5230913042e3?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=17018&rangeEnd=17060"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840995_18_4338-4384",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "4338-4384",
      "markText": "中国的过去，禁忌特多，所以说话作文时有隐晦，或指彼而喻此，或借古以讽今，这在明朝人更为惯技。",
      "totalCount": 6732,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840995&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=4338&rangeEnd=4384",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/091322d05cd5230913042e3?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=4338&rangeEnd=4384"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840995_19_6503-6558",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "6503-6558",
      "markText": "负责纠察的御史开始点名，并且记下咳嗽、吐痰等以至牙笏坠地、步履不稳重等等属于“失仪”范围的官员姓名，听候参处。",
      "totalCount": 6579,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840995&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=6503&rangeEnd=6558",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/091322d05cd5230913042e3?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=6503&rangeEnd=6558"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840995_20_24791-24838",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "24791-24838",
      "markText": "技术上的争端，一经发展，就可以升级扩大而成道德问题，胜利者及失败者也就相应地被认为至善或极恶。",
